288
00:13:28,510 --> 00:13:29,310
Ji Tanyin.

289
00:13:31,230 --> 00:13:32,110
He's calling me.

290
00:13:32,310 --> 00:13:33,310
I have to go now.

291
00:13:34,550 --> 00:13:35,980
I haven't finished speaking yet.

292
00:13:37,430 --> 00:13:38,230
Ji Tanyin.

293
00:13:42,390 --> 00:13:43,270
High Priest.

294
00:13:43,510 --> 00:13:44,310
Are you busy with something?

295
00:13:45,630 --> 00:13:46,510
Then come with me.

296
00:14:01,470 --> 00:14:02,310
High Priest,

297
00:14:02,650 --> 00:14:03,950
you wield the Divine Left Hand

298
00:14:03,950 --> 00:14:05,190
and bear a demigod's form.

299
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:06,670
Illness should never touch you.

300
00:14:06,870 --> 00:14:08,750
Yet the golden hoop binds you,

301
00:14:09,020 --> 00:14:10,550
stripping your magical power

302
00:14:10,550 --> 00:14:12,190
and rendering you no different from a mortal,

303
00:14:12,190 --> 00:14:13,660
vulnerable to exhaustion and sickness.

304
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:15,070
So?

305
00:14:15,090 --> 00:14:16,480
So you shouldn't put it on.

306
00:14:20,940 --> 00:14:22,130
-High Priest.
-High Priest.

307
00:14:26,140 --> 00:14:27,460
They fear you greatly.

308
00:14:27,630 --> 00:14:29,270
They say you are cruel,

309
00:14:29,270 --> 00:14:31,150
unpredictable, and volatile in temper.

310
00:14:31,390 --> 00:14:33,510
They say you live in extravagant indulgence,

311
00:14:33,510 --> 00:14:34,430
lost in endless debauchery.

312
00:14:34,430 --> 00:14:35,710
You are not only ruthless and lustful

313
00:14:35,710 --> 00:14:37,030
but also greedy and excessive.

314
00:14:37,190 --> 00:14:38,830
You drink a hundred jars of wine a day,

315
00:14:38,910 --> 00:14:39,670
and at the slightest displeasure,

316
00:14:39,670 --> 00:14:40,960
you take lives without hesitation.

317
00:14:41,670 --> 00:14:42,590
A hundred jars?

318
00:14:44,230 --> 00:14:45,670
That's quite a capacity.

319
00:14:46,780 --> 00:14:47,950
Aren't you angry?

320
00:14:49,150 --> 00:14:50,270
Why would I be angry?

321
00:14:50,630 --> 00:14:51,590
They misunderstand you.

322
00:14:51,590 --> 00:14:52,870
They even slander you.

323
00:14:53,790 --> 00:14:55,230
Greed, anger, delusion, arrogance, and doubt

324
00:14:56,190 --> 00:14:57,270
lead to misdeeds

325
00:14:57,420 --> 00:14:58,510
and hinder the cultivation.

326
00:14:58,790 --> 00:14:59,870
Seeking enlightenment and refining the heart

327
00:15:00,190 --> 00:15:01,630
has always been my lesson.

328
00:15:02,030 --> 00:15:03,020
What they say about me

329
00:15:03,430 --> 00:15:05,030
has nothing to do with me.

330
00:15:07,990 --> 00:15:09,470
Why do you care so much about me?

331
00:15:10,070 --> 00:15:10,950
Zi Fei said

332
00:15:11,230 --> 00:15:12,320
you admire me.

333
00:15:12,320 --> 00:15:13,110
Admire?

334
00:15:14,540 --> 00:15:15,380
Thinking about it carefully,

335
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:16,990
it seems like from the very beginning,

336
00:15:17,410 --> 00:15:18,730
you knew who I was.

337
00:15:19,110 --> 00:15:20,830
That day, at the selection for handmaidens,

338
00:15:21,020 --> 00:15:22,270
when you saw me appear,

339
00:15:22,860 --> 00:15:24,350
you weren't surprised in the slightest.

340
00:15:25,740 --> 00:15:27,230
I've heard that many human women

341
00:15:27,230 --> 00:15:28,230
adore Tanghua,

342
00:15:28,750 --> 00:15:30,350
going to great lengths

343
00:15:30,990 --> 00:15:32,070
to enter his Jinxia Palace.

344
00:15:32,110 --> 00:15:32,950
I never thought

345
00:15:33,790 --> 00:15:35,150
I'd experience this myself.

346
00:15:35,740 --> 00:15:37,030
Don't overthink it.

347
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:38,310
I'm not like them.

348
00:15:40,030 --> 00:15:40,830
Alright.

349
00:15:44,070 --> 00:15:45,150
You're leaving just like that?

350
00:15:46,830 --> 00:15:48,020
I haven't even finished speaking.

351
00:15:57,110 --> 00:15:57,900
Give it to me.

352
00:15:58,230 --> 00:15:59,500
I'll take it in for you.

353
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:00,270
No need.

354
00:16:12,110 --> 00:16:12,840
Does he have to read

355
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:13,950
so many books every day?

356
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:15,670
It's part of his studies,

357
00:16:15,670 --> 00:16:16,950
which aids in his cultivation.

358
00:16:17,470 --> 00:16:18,630
Do you believe that too?

359
00:17:37,230 --> 00:17:38,030
You're here.

360
00:17:40,710 --> 00:17:42,060
I still have some things to write down.

361
00:17:42,350 --> 00:17:43,390
I'll speak with you later.

362
00:17:56,590 --> 00:17:57,710
You're from the immortal race.

363
00:17:58,110 --> 00:17:59,690
Does reading so many books help you?

364
00:17:59,790 --> 00:18:00,550
Of course.

365
00:18:01,120 --> 00:18:02,200
Books are like medicine.

366
00:18:02,510 --> 00:18:04,590
Reading them can dispel ignorance.

367
00:18:07,150 --> 00:18:08,590
So ignorance is a sin too.

368
00:18:08,780 --> 00:18:09,660
Is that so?

369
00:18:11,470 --> 00:18:12,390
That's exactly right.

370
00:18:12,670 --> 00:18:14,430
Ignorance is also a sin.

371
00:18:28,870 --> 00:18:29,670
Young Master,

372
00:18:31,600 --> 00:18:32,790
the Council of Elders has increased patrols

373
00:18:32,790 --> 00:18:34,150
in the clan,

374
00:18:34,550 --> 00:18:36,870
and the mountain's protective formation has been activated.

375
00:18:37,310 --> 00:18:40,030
Can they really deal with the War Demon

376
00:18:40,670 --> 00:18:42,150
with just those formations and guards?

377
00:18:42,340 --> 00:18:43,630
The Council of Elders believes they can.

378
00:18:45,440 --> 00:18:47,430
Young Master, look.

379
00:18:51,350 --> 00:18:52,920
How is the clan reacting now?

380
00:18:52,940 --> 00:18:54,770
They are in a state of panic, seeing danger in every shadow.

381
00:18:55,190 --> 00:18:56,230
The Council of Elders has urgently recalled

382
00:18:56,230 --> 00:18:57,830
all members from outside

383
00:18:57,980 --> 00:18:59,810
and is searching everywhere for traces of the War Demon.

384
00:19:00,350 --> 00:19:01,630
Anyone suspicious

385
00:19:01,630 --> 00:19:03,020
is to be captured first and questioned later.

386
00:19:03,020 --> 00:19:04,430
They've even dispatched people among humans

387
00:19:04,430 --> 00:19:05,510
to gather intelligence.

388
00:19:06,070 --> 00:19:06,870
In any case,

389
00:19:07,340 --> 00:19:08,630
they're already afraid.

390
00:19:11,150 --> 00:19:11,950
Are they?

391
00:19:13,110 --> 00:19:14,350
Good. That's enough.

392
00:19:27,590 --> 00:19:28,790
Where are you going?

393
00:19:29,540 --> 00:19:30,500
Today is the day to ascend Tianqu Peak

394
00:19:30,500 --> 00:19:31,630
for spirit refinement.

395
00:19:31,710 --> 00:19:32,510
Spirit refinement?

396
00:19:35,550 --> 00:19:36,550
This is a snack,

397
00:19:36,550 --> 00:19:38,180
freshly delivered from Xiaoxiang Peak.

398
00:19:39,500 --> 00:19:40,830
I'll have it when I return.

399
00:19:44,590 --> 00:19:45,870
Are you feeling unwell?

400
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:18,550
So this is the Liujiao Palace.

401
00:20:19,150 --> 00:20:20,830
It's truly magnificent.

402
00:20:22,150 --> 00:20:22,950
Tanyin.

403
00:20:24,790 --> 00:20:26,070
Why are you here?

404
00:20:26,390 --> 00:20:27,710
I've joined Yaoxiang Peak

405
00:20:27,790 --> 00:20:29,790
and now follow Elder Xinyao.

406
00:20:30,590 --> 00:20:32,390
I came to deliver medicine to the High Priest.

407
00:20:34,150 --> 00:20:36,350
I heard the High Priest's in poor health

408
00:20:36,510 --> 00:20:37,470
and must take Elder Xinyao's refined pills

409
00:20:37,470 --> 00:20:39,200
every month.

410
00:20:40,230 --> 00:20:41,400
I never thought that

411
00:20:41,590 --> 00:20:43,160
even with a demigod's body,

412
00:20:43,270 --> 00:20:44,630
he could still fall ill.

413
00:20:45,830 --> 00:20:46,510
Oh, and inside,

414
00:20:46,510 --> 00:20:47,910
there's also a flask of medicinal wine.

415
00:20:47,910 --> 00:20:48,750
Elder Xinyao

416
00:20:48,750 --> 00:20:49,790
specifically instructed the High Priest

417
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:51,230
to drink it before bed.

418
00:20:51,230 --> 00:20:52,380
It helps with sleep.

419
00:20:54,080 --> 00:20:55,160
Then I'll be going.

420
00:21:07,190 --> 00:21:08,360
You want to kill Yuanzhong?

421
00:21:09,960 --> 00:21:11,370
This poison may be potent,

422
00:21:11,940 --> 00:21:13,110
but it won't be enough to kill him.

423
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:20,830
The Nailed Seven Arrows Curse

424
00:21:21,030 --> 00:21:21,950
is indeed a formidable

425
00:21:21,950 --> 00:21:23,030
cursing technique.

426
00:21:23,030 --> 00:21:23,830
But sadly,

427
00:21:24,210 --> 00:21:25,700
your method is flawed.

428
00:21:27,800 --> 00:21:29,290
So it was you who took it.

429
00:21:29,350 --> 00:21:30,190
If not for me,

430
00:21:30,190 --> 00:21:31,590
you would have been captured that day.

431
00:21:31,710 --> 00:21:32,680
What do you want?

432
00:21:32,710 --> 00:21:33,830
I don't want anything.

433
00:21:34,440 --> 00:21:35,230
But

434
00:21:35,790 --> 00:21:36,790
you cannot kill him.

435
00:21:36,790 --> 00:21:37,990
He is an evil spirit,

436
00:21:38,290 --> 00:21:40,000
cruel and bloodthirsty, enslaving entire races.

437
00:21:40,070 --> 00:21:40,780
Over the years,

438
00:21:40,780 --> 00:21:42,190
how many humans have died under the oppression

439
00:21:42,190 --> 00:21:43,150
of the Youhu Clan?

440
00:21:43,190 --> 00:21:44,540
They see themselves as gods,

441
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:45,910
treating us like ants and livestock,

442
00:21:45,910 --> 00:21:46,820
to be crushed

443
00:21:46,820 --> 00:21:47,910
and slaughtered at will.

444
00:21:50,550 --> 00:21:51,470
This is a method I learned

445
00:21:51,470 --> 00:21:52,550
from ancient books.

446
00:21:53,410 --> 00:21:54,470
As long as I stay

447
00:21:54,470 --> 00:21:55,100
within 10 miles of my enemy,

448
00:21:55,100 --> 00:21:56,390
silently recite their name,

449
00:21:56,390 --> 00:21:57,110
bind grass into a human shape,

450
00:21:57,110 --> 00:21:58,070
and bow three times a day

451
00:21:58,070 --> 00:21:59,350
for 21 consecutive days,

452
00:21:59,430 --> 00:22:00,470
I can scatter their three souls

453
00:22:00,470 --> 00:22:01,480
and seven spirits.

454
00:22:01,670 --> 00:22:02,980
Then, I will have my revenge.

455
00:22:03,870 --> 00:22:04,950
I went through so much hardship

456
00:22:04,950 --> 00:22:05,910
just to get here.

457
00:22:05,930 --> 00:22:06,960
If not for you,

458
00:22:07,880 --> 00:22:09,200
I would have already succeeded.

459
00:22:09,270 --> 00:22:10,230
I told you,

460
00:22:10,470 --> 00:22:11,820
your steps are incomplete.

461
00:22:11,820 --> 00:22:12,990
Even if you bow until your back breaks,

462
00:22:12,990 --> 00:22:13,950
you won't succeed.

463
00:22:13,950 --> 00:22:14,670
And besides,

464
00:22:14,670 --> 00:22:15,710
he is not a bad person.

465
00:22:16,390 --> 00:22:17,950
What you speak of has nothing to do with him.

466
00:22:18,230 --> 00:22:19,030
He should not be

467
00:22:19,030 --> 00:22:20,190
the target of your hatred.

468
00:22:20,550 --> 00:22:21,670
I will say this one last time.

469
00:22:22,050 --> 00:22:23,110
If this happens again,

470
00:22:23,230 --> 00:22:24,510
I will not cover for you.

471
00:22:25,070 --> 00:22:25,870
Now leave.

472
00:22:27,950 --> 00:22:29,350
You're human too.

473
00:22:30,390 --> 00:22:32,030
Why are you defending our enemy?

474
00:22:32,990 --> 00:22:34,070
Is he really an enemy?

475
00:22:34,100 --> 00:22:34,740
Yes.

476
00:22:35,430 --> 00:22:37,150
He is the High Priest of the Youhu Clan.

477
00:22:37,350 --> 00:22:38,430
He possesses the Divine Left Hand,

478
00:22:38,430 --> 00:22:39,550
wielding a force vast enough

479
00:22:39,550 --> 00:22:41,000
to upheave the heavens and shatter the earth.

480
00:22:41,110 --> 00:22:42,910
Why do you insist on protecting him?

481
00:22:43,780 --> 00:22:45,400
Should someone be condemned simply for having power?

482
00:23:02,790 --> 00:23:03,630
What's wrong with him?

483
00:23:04,280 --> 00:23:05,080
It's nothing.

484
00:23:17,710 --> 00:23:18,670
Madam Zhi Dai.

485
00:23:23,910 --> 00:23:24,790
It's so late.

486
00:23:24,870 --> 00:23:25,790
Where have you been?

487
00:23:26,470 --> 00:23:28,030
I was sent by Elder Xinyao

488
00:23:28,030 --> 00:23:29,500
to deliver medicine to the Liujiao Palace.

489
00:23:31,110 --> 00:23:32,750
Madam Zhi Dai, I have things to do.

490
00:23:32,770 --> 00:23:33,720
I'll take my leave.

491
00:24:02,670 --> 00:24:03,750
What's really going on with him?

492
00:24:04,630 --> 00:24:05,630
He's still not doing well.

493
00:24:06,470 --> 00:24:07,230
Stay here and watch over him.

494
00:24:07,230 --> 00:24:07,870
I'll go to Yaoxiang Peak

495
00:24:07,870 --> 00:24:09,070
to invite Elder Xinyao over.

496
00:24:12,110 --> 00:24:12,910
High Priest.

497
00:24:20,470 --> 00:24:21,590
Why is your body so cold?

498
00:24:23,070 --> 00:24:24,270
Are you ill?

499
00:24:26,770 --> 00:24:28,050
It's my studies.

500
00:24:29,150 --> 00:24:30,630
Is this part of your cultivation too?

501
00:24:34,550 --> 00:24:35,350
High Priest!

502
00:24:36,350 --> 00:24:37,150
High Priest.

503
00:24:39,350 --> 00:24:40,190
High Priest.

504
00:24:54,240 --> 00:24:55,030
Here she comes.

505
00:25:06,910 --> 00:25:09,070
He's lost too much blood, and his pulse is weak.

506
00:25:09,370 --> 00:25:11,050
The Divine Left Hand is saving him now.

507
00:25:11,790 --> 00:25:12,470
Elder Dingxu has changed

508
00:25:12,470 --> 00:25:13,550
the spirit refinement sessions from once every ten days

509
00:25:13,550 --> 00:25:14,670
to once every five days.

510
00:25:14,670 --> 00:25:15,710
That's too much for his body to endure.

511
00:25:15,710 --> 00:25:16,240
Why didn't you

512
00:25:16,240 --> 00:25:17,510
tell me earlier?

513
00:25:17,750 --> 00:25:18,540
Yuanzhong said

514
00:25:18,710 --> 00:25:19,910
it aids his cultivation

515
00:25:19,910 --> 00:25:20,880
and forbade me from informing you.

516
00:25:20,990 --> 00:25:21,790
You people...

517
00:25:38,110 --> 00:25:39,430
Quick, help him out of the medicinal bath.

518
00:25:39,550 --> 00:25:40,910
The potency of the medicine is too strong.

519
00:25:40,910 --> 00:25:41,830
His body is too weak

520
00:25:41,830 --> 00:25:42,710
to endure it.

521
00:25:44,030 --> 00:25:44,830
Go on ahead.

522
00:25:44,830 --> 00:25:45,950
Boil some more hot water in the kitchen.

523
00:26:09,200 --> 00:26:13,600
[Liujiao Palace]

524
00:26:22,170 --> 00:26:23,250
Is he feeling better?

525
00:26:23,470 --> 00:26:24,550
What are you doing here?

526
00:26:24,550 --> 00:26:25,510
Elder Xinyao is inside.

527
00:26:25,510 --> 00:26:26,510
He'll be fine.

528
00:26:28,470 --> 00:26:29,630
What is spirit refinement?

529
00:26:30,070 --> 00:26:31,190
It is part of his studies.

530
00:26:31,950 --> 00:26:33,190
It is a secret technique of our clan.

531
00:26:33,190 --> 00:26:34,070
I cannot tell you.

532
00:26:34,910 --> 00:26:36,390
You don't have to keep watch here the whole time.

533
00:26:57,180 --> 00:26:58,940
Dingxu has changed the spirit refinement schedule.

534
00:26:59,830 --> 00:27:01,470
Why didn't you tell me?

535
00:27:02,430 --> 00:27:04,230
Well, now you know, don't you?

536
00:27:06,950 --> 00:27:08,230
Do you really think

537
00:27:08,780 --> 00:27:10,230
this training is useful to you?

538
00:27:12,950 --> 00:27:13,750
Yes.

539
00:27:15,230 --> 00:27:16,750
And it is of great use.

540
00:27:17,900 --> 00:27:19,100
Humans have five sins:

541
00:27:20,220 --> 00:27:21,100
cruelty,

542
00:27:21,670 --> 00:27:22,550
obsession,

543
00:27:23,710 --> 00:27:24,510
hypocrisy,

544
00:27:25,230 --> 00:27:26,030
jealousy,

545
00:27:26,990 --> 00:27:27,790
and ignorance.

546
00:27:28,470 --> 00:27:30,310
Only through diligent cultivation,

547
00:27:31,000 --> 00:27:32,280
aligning knowledge with action,

548
00:27:33,000 --> 00:27:34,710
can one rid themselves of the Five Sins

549
00:27:35,670 --> 00:27:37,060
and attain divinity.

550
00:27:38,260 --> 00:27:40,270
My talent and insight

551
00:27:40,710 --> 00:27:42,110
are quite remarkable.

552
00:27:43,830 --> 00:27:45,510
And with the Divine Left Hand,

553
00:27:47,110 --> 00:27:48,110
I believe

554
00:27:49,130 --> 00:27:50,990
I will eventually find a way

555
00:27:51,840 --> 00:27:53,400
to comprehend the Great Way.

556
00:27:54,900 --> 00:27:55,700
You...

557
00:27:55,720 --> 00:27:57,330
Elder Xinyao, don't worry.

558
00:27:58,670 --> 00:28:00,550
These are all necessary steps.

559
00:28:02,190 --> 00:28:03,230
I can handle it.

560
00:28:07,550 --> 00:28:08,990
Then you should rest well.

561
00:28:09,560 --> 00:28:10,600
I'll be going now.

562
00:28:11,630 --> 00:28:12,750
Take care, Elder.

563
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:39,150
High Priest, are you hungry?

564
00:28:41,270 --> 00:28:42,110
A little.

565
00:28:42,470 --> 00:28:43,430
What would you like to eat?

566
00:28:47,220 --> 00:28:48,430
Red Oil Cloud Strings.

567
00:28:49,820 --> 00:28:50,660
W-What?

568
00:28:52,710 --> 00:28:55,990
It's when you soak the cloud strings in water,

569
00:28:56,910 --> 00:28:58,550
drain them after a while,

570
00:28:59,390 --> 00:29:01,110
then cut red peppers into thin strips,

571
00:29:02,030 --> 00:29:05,630
add salt, sugar, and other seasonings,

572
00:29:06,390 --> 00:29:08,950
pour hot oil over it, and stir well.

573
00:29:10,270 --> 00:29:11,550
What are cloud strings?

574
00:29:16,110 --> 00:29:17,640
What about Kidney Bean Immortal Soup?

