Grain Rain Tofu?

576
00:29:24,700 --> 00:29:25,700
Never mind then.

577
00:29:28,110 --> 00:29:28,900
Porridge?

578
00:29:30,030 --> 00:29:30,910
Is porridge okay?

579
00:29:33,550 --> 00:29:34,340
Sure.

580
00:29:34,710 --> 00:29:35,750
Wait for me a moment.

581
00:29:44,750 --> 00:29:45,550
High Priest,

582
00:29:45,780 --> 00:29:46,900
have you ever thought

583
00:29:46,950 --> 00:29:48,590
that everything they told you might be a lie?

584
00:29:58,630 --> 00:29:59,410
Doubt

585
00:30:00,590 --> 00:30:02,070
is also a form of obsession.

586
00:30:03,440 --> 00:30:04,730
Obsession is a sin.

587
00:30:29,070 --> 00:30:31,190
How have you been settling in at the Liujiao Palace?

588
00:30:32,270 --> 00:30:33,070
It's been good.

589
00:30:34,190 --> 00:30:35,190
What about the High Priest?

590
00:30:35,510 --> 00:30:36,550
How does he treat you?

591
00:30:37,590 --> 00:30:38,430
Not bad.

592
00:30:41,790 --> 00:30:43,070
Did you come to see me today

593
00:30:43,390 --> 00:30:44,350
because of something?

594
00:30:46,790 --> 00:30:47,750
There is indeed something.

595
00:30:48,310 --> 00:30:49,230
Do you remember

596
00:30:49,430 --> 00:30:50,950
someone was performing curses

597
00:30:50,950 --> 00:30:52,190
at Xiaoxiang Peak before?

598
00:30:52,510 --> 00:30:54,110
I even searched your room back then.

599
00:30:54,830 --> 00:30:56,270
At that moment, I found nothing.

600
00:30:56,750 --> 00:30:57,670
But yesterday,

601
00:30:57,740 --> 00:30:59,340
I ran into Lyu Yao on the road.

602
00:30:59,870 --> 00:31:01,950
She looked panicked and terrified.

603
00:31:02,300 --> 00:31:03,590
So I followed her.

604
00:31:04,390 --> 00:31:06,230
Guess what I found?

605
00:31:10,060 --> 00:31:10,870
She said

606
00:31:11,410 --> 00:31:13,210
it was you covering for her.

607
00:31:18,030 --> 00:31:19,030
Over the years,

608
00:31:19,510 --> 00:31:21,070
we have had frequent clashes

609
00:31:21,070 --> 00:31:22,110
with the Youhu Clan.

610
00:31:22,910 --> 00:31:24,670
The Youhu people pride themselves on their status,

611
00:31:24,800 --> 00:31:26,290
claiming to be saviors.

612
00:31:26,790 --> 00:31:27,780
Our people

613
00:31:27,780 --> 00:31:29,290
no longer wish to continue serving them.

614
00:31:30,150 --> 00:31:31,510
Some of the more radical members

615
00:31:31,510 --> 00:31:32,830
have made it their goal to take down the Youhu Clan

616
00:31:32,930 --> 00:31:34,570
and kill the High Priest.

617
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:36,310
It's not the first time

618
00:31:36,310 --> 00:31:37,590
they've sent assassins up the mountain.

619
00:31:37,920 --> 00:31:38,740
Clearly,

620
00:31:38,920 --> 00:31:40,310
Lyu Yao is one of those people.

621
00:31:41,070 --> 00:31:42,430
But what I'm curious about is,

622
00:31:42,910 --> 00:31:44,600
who are you?

623
00:31:53,850 --> 00:31:54,930
I've investigated you.

624
00:31:55,430 --> 00:31:56,510
Your background is clean,

625
00:31:56,510 --> 00:31:57,620
and your family is well-regarded.

626
00:31:57,910 --> 00:31:59,070
You seem like

627
00:31:59,070 --> 00:32:00,630
a well-mannered young lady

628
00:32:00,630 --> 00:32:01,750
who doesn't go out much.

629
00:32:02,590 --> 00:32:03,390
But,

630
00:32:04,350 --> 00:32:06,370
who taught you your craftsmanship?

631
00:32:07,190 --> 00:32:08,870
In our human race, craftsmanship is highly esteemed.

632
00:32:08,980 --> 00:32:10,860
Each province and county has a craft school,

633
00:32:11,590 --> 00:32:13,680
and all craftsmen must be registered.

634
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:15,510
You never attended school,

635
00:32:15,590 --> 00:32:16,790
nor did you apprentice.

636
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:18,430
So, where did

637
00:32:18,430 --> 00:32:19,990
your extraordinary craftsmanship

638
00:32:19,990 --> 00:32:21,270
come from?

639
00:32:29,060 --> 00:32:30,070
Why are you smiling?

640
00:32:31,360 --> 00:32:32,410
Madam Zhi Dai,

641
00:32:33,230 --> 00:32:34,830
do you have a favor to ask of me?

642
00:32:38,340 --> 00:32:39,750
If you're just suspicious of me,

643
00:32:40,060 --> 00:32:41,350
you have Lyu Yao in your hands.

644
00:32:41,370 --> 00:32:42,480
You could just expose me.

645
00:32:43,080 --> 00:32:44,840
Why bother coming here to interrogate me?

646
00:32:55,570 --> 00:32:56,750
What do you want?

647
00:32:56,950 --> 00:32:58,190
Why don't you just say it?

648
00:32:58,750 --> 00:32:59,950
Perhaps I can help.

649
00:33:00,830 --> 00:33:01,550
But if you

650
00:33:01,550 --> 00:33:02,830
keep beating around the bush,

651
00:33:03,190 --> 00:33:04,510
I'll lose interest in listening.

652
00:33:06,750 --> 00:33:07,920
I want to ask for your help

653
00:33:08,650 --> 00:33:10,580
to unlock this Two-Form Immobilizing Bracelet.

654
00:33:19,780 --> 00:33:20,590
You're awake.

655
00:33:23,990 --> 00:33:25,590
Are you going to Tianqu Peak again?

656
00:33:28,430 --> 00:33:29,430
Don't go.

657
00:33:29,510 --> 00:33:31,070
You still look weak.

658
00:33:31,460 --> 00:33:32,590
I'm much better now.

659
00:33:33,930 --> 00:33:35,040
Is it a must?

660
00:33:37,150 --> 00:33:38,070
Yes, it is.

661
00:33:40,270 --> 00:33:41,230
Then I'll go with you.

662
00:33:50,430 --> 00:33:51,580
I was right.

663
00:33:52,300 --> 00:33:53,620
She really has taken a liking to you.

664
00:34:11,550 --> 00:34:13,230
Sit up here, and I'll push you.

665
00:34:13,790 --> 00:34:14,750
Lying down for a few days

666
00:34:15,110 --> 00:34:16,219
has left my bones all stiff.

667
00:34:20,860 --> 00:34:22,170
How does the spirit refinement at Tianqu Peak

668
00:34:22,429 --> 00:34:23,550
differ from

669
00:34:23,550 --> 00:34:24,699
your usual practice?

670
00:34:25,739 --> 00:34:28,170
Spirit refinement tests my willpower.

671
00:34:29,639 --> 00:34:30,510
Is it difficult?

672
00:34:32,150 --> 00:34:32,989
It's manageable.

673
00:34:34,070 --> 00:34:34,710
But that day,

674
00:34:34,710 --> 00:34:35,989
you were already unconscious

675
00:34:36,070 --> 00:34:37,590
and lay in the room for three days.

676
00:34:37,920 --> 00:34:39,070
It's part of the test;

677
00:34:39,710 --> 00:34:41,070
hardships are inevitable.

678
00:34:43,830 --> 00:34:44,630
By the way,

679
00:34:45,219 --> 00:34:46,510
when you came to Fangwai Mountain,

680
00:34:46,790 --> 00:34:47,870
did you pass through Baisha Bay

681
00:34:48,350 --> 00:34:49,750
and try the pricky fruit there?

682
00:34:50,429 --> 00:34:51,469
What is that?

683
00:34:51,830 --> 00:34:53,150
It's black in color,

684
00:34:53,489 --> 00:34:54,810
only about the size of a fingernail.

685
00:34:55,350 --> 00:34:56,400
It's sour and astringent at first,

686
00:34:56,630 --> 00:34:57,590
but it has a sweet aftertaste.

687
00:34:57,990 --> 00:34:58,940
It's really tasty.

688
00:35:03,270 --> 00:35:04,630
What a shame, then.

689
00:35:10,990 --> 00:35:11,920
High Priest,

690
00:35:14,590 --> 00:35:16,110
you're late today.

691
00:35:16,790 --> 00:35:17,710
I overslept.

692
00:35:17,950 --> 00:35:19,370
Spirit refinement is crucial.

693
00:35:19,410 --> 00:35:20,850
Elder Dingxu once emphasized

694
00:35:21,000 --> 00:35:22,370
the importance of being punctual.

695
00:35:27,760 --> 00:35:28,750
Wait for me here.

696
00:35:29,340 --> 00:35:30,750
Can't I go in with you?

697
00:35:39,930 --> 00:35:42,690
[No Trespassing] [Offenders Will Be Punished]

698
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:44,670
Please wait here, High Priest.

699
00:36:44,750 --> 00:36:46,430
I'll go notify Elder Dingxu.

700
00:36:58,950 --> 00:36:59,780
Let me out!

701
00:36:59,830 --> 00:37:00,660
Let me out!

702
00:37:00,790 --> 00:37:01,780
Let me out!

703
00:37:02,160 --> 00:37:03,600
Let me out!

704
00:37:04,870 --> 00:37:06,430
Let me out!

705
00:37:45,950 --> 00:37:46,750
High Priest,

706
00:37:49,070 --> 00:37:49,870
sorry to keep you waiting.

707
00:37:51,390 --> 00:37:52,190
What's wrong?

708
00:38:09,070 --> 00:38:10,390
How's your rest been

709
00:38:10,750 --> 00:38:11,870
these past few days?

710
00:38:13,910 --> 00:38:14,710
It's been good.

711
00:38:15,070 --> 00:38:16,670
I heard that after you went back last time,

712
00:38:16,670 --> 00:38:17,380
Elder Xinyao

713
00:38:17,380 --> 00:38:18,870
went to the Liujiao Palace overnight.

714
00:38:19,630 --> 00:38:21,230
Is there something wrong with your body?

715
00:38:22,070 --> 00:38:23,710
You don't look well.

716
00:38:24,150 --> 00:38:26,070
Do you need to rest for a few more days?

717
00:38:27,550 --> 00:38:28,620
To refine the spirit and grasp the path to enlightenment,

718
00:38:29,310 --> 00:38:32,070
every fleeting day of delay is a loss to me.

719
00:38:35,790 --> 00:38:37,300
Congratulations, High Priest.

720
00:38:37,550 --> 00:38:38,500
It seems like your enlightenment

721
00:38:38,540 --> 00:38:40,170
has deepened again.

722
00:38:41,910 --> 00:38:42,700
Let's begin.

723
00:38:43,270 --> 00:38:44,070
Yes.

724
00:39:05,510 --> 00:39:06,510
How is it now?

725
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:09,110
Does it hurt a lot?

726
00:39:20,870 --> 00:39:22,140
It's already noon.

727
00:39:22,140 --> 00:39:23,760
When will he come out?

728
00:39:24,580 --> 00:39:25,750
Once the spirit refinement is finished,

729
00:39:26,070 --> 00:39:27,230
he'll naturally come out.

730
00:39:27,910 --> 00:39:29,550
Then when will it end?

731
00:39:32,150 --> 00:39:33,270
It's hard to say.

732
00:39:35,860 --> 00:39:37,430
It could be two or three hours,

733
00:39:37,580 --> 00:39:40,060
but it could also take a whole day and night.

734
00:39:40,190 --> 00:39:41,870
How many tests does he have to go through

735
00:39:41,870 --> 00:39:43,150
before he can complete the spirit refinement?

736
00:39:46,150 --> 00:39:47,670
His body is still very weak.

737
00:39:47,790 --> 00:39:49,190
I'm afraid he won't last long.

738
00:39:49,710 --> 00:39:51,230
Can it end earlier?

739
00:40:26,150 --> 00:40:27,510
Master, it's enough.

740
00:40:34,910 --> 00:40:37,350
Let's stop here for today.

